	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you can you should get a ride over to Greater Faydark and maybe solo the orcs out in the fields. Or, you can go into Crushbone and get in a good group for hunting the orcs. For soloing you should use the Earth pet befors level 8, but most of the time when you group you should use the air pet, or if you are fighting mainly caster types you should use the Air type. Fire type is also good for soloing but not until 8 or above. If you cant get a port to Gfay then you should at least go to Qeynos hills and Blackburrow until level 8 and then at 8 go to wisp Island and solo the wisps there. We are probably the only class that can solo them at level 8 too. If you dont like grouping you can probably solo until about level 50-55 if you are good at it.<br><br>Dalaan Ogrebane 60th Crusader-Sol Ro<br>Heiggan Stackbabber 59th Assassin-Sol Ro<br>Eaein O'Malley 49th Mage-Sol Ro<br>Dallaan 14th Paladin-Torvo<br>Eaein 8th Mage-Torvo<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
